verbose_text: Compared with the V. axillare high-dose + PMA group, V. axillare high-dose group further reduced the expression of TNF-alpha, IkappaBalpha, and IKKbeta mRNA (P < 0.05, P < 0.01; Figures XREF_FIG - XREF_FIG), and the downregulation of NF-kappaB and IKKbeta was more than that of the V. axillare low-dose group (P < 0.05; Figures XREF_FIG and XREF_FIG).
